  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4587136/" class="title-link">喜欢历史的这系列曾文正全集不推荐买</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4587136"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/2164580/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2164580-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2164580/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">tradition</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-01-17"
      class="main-meta">2011-01-17 23:10:18</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4587136_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  买这个版本的要注意，一此套曾文正公全集没有家书，其次日记也收的少的可怜，但一般全集不收的十八家诗钞和经史百家杂钞之类不是曾直接所著而只是其编的却占了五本之多。单从史料来看的话，此套全集不怎么样，但如果你喜欢文学之类而不是考虑其史学价值的，到不妨一买

